Interface GraphQueryBuilderFinalizer<E extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface GraphQueryBuilderFinalizer<E extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element>
    Defines the last step in the fluent graph query builder API.
